ActCanada Transportation Act
PrecisORDER AUTHORIZING PERSONS SPECIFIED THEREIN TO BE PARTIES TO CERTAIN COMMERCIAL ARRANGEMENTS AND PROVIDING SPECIFIC DIRECTIVES TO THE VANCOUVER PORT AUTHORITY AND THE FRASER RIVER PORT AUTHORITY - which authorizes for-hire truck operators and owner-operators, shippers, brokers and the Port Authorities to adhere to the July 29, 2005 Memorandum of Agreement in respect of rates, charges and terms and conditions without the constraints imposed under the Competition Act.
